#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn45.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Avijjāvagga "
msgstr "1. Ignorance "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 7. Dutiyaaññatarabhikkhusutta → dutiyabhikkhusuttaṃ (bj) | aññataro bhikkhu 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Dutiyaaññatarabhikkhusutta "
msgstr "7. A Mendicant (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.7:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.7:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn45.7:2.1"
msgid "“‘Rāgavinayo dosavinayo mohavinayo’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of ‘the removal of greed, hate, and delusion’. "

msgctxt "sn45.7:2.2"
msgid "Kissa nu kho etaṃ, bhante, adhivacanaṃ: "
msgstr "What is this a term for?” "

msgctxt "sn45.7:2.3"
msgid "‘rāgavinayo dosavinayo mohavinayo’”ti? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.7:2.4"
msgid "“Nibbānadhātuyā kho etaṃ, bhikkhu, adhivacanaṃ: "
msgstr "“Mendicant, the removal of greed, hate, and delusion is a term for the natural principle of extinguishment. "

msgctxt "sn45.7:2.5"
msgid "‘rāgavinayo dosavinayo mohavinayo’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn45.7:2.6"
msgid "Āsavānaṃ khayo tena vuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "It’s used to speak of the ending of defilements.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn45.7:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, the mendicant said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.7:3.2"
msgid "“‘amataṃ, amatan’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of ‘the deathless’. "

msgctxt "sn45.7:3.3"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho, bhante, amataṃ, katamo amatagāmimaggo”ti? "
msgstr "What is the deathless? And what is the path that leads to the deathless?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.7:3.4"
msgid "“Yo kho, bhikkhu, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—"
msgstr "“The ending of greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn45.7:3.5"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati amataṃ. "
msgstr "This is called the deathless. "

msgctxt "sn45.7:3.6"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo amatagāmimaggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "The path that leads to the deathless is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "

msgctxt "sn45.7:3.7"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhī”ti. "
msgstr "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.7:3.8"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

